{
  "page": "Bandallon",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;background: #DEDEE2;\">Bandallon</th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\nCastle</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Location</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Reach\" title=\"Reach\">Reach</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Westeros\" title=\"Westeros\">Westeros</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Government</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/House_Blackbar\" title=\"House Blackbar\">House Blackbar</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Feudalism\" title=\"Feudalism\">feudal lord</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Religion</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Faith_of_the_Seven\" title=\"Faith of the Seven\">Faith of the Seven</a></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\">\n<div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:402px;\">\n<div style=\"position: relative; border: 1px solid lightgray\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:The_Reach.png\" class=\"image\" title=\"The Reach and the location of Bandallon\"><img alt=\"The Reach and the location of Bandallon\" src=\"/images/thumb/8/89/The_Reach.png/400px-The_Reach.png\" width=\"400\" height=\"513\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/8/89/The_Reach.png/600px-The_Reach.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/8/89/The_Reach.png/800px-The_Reach.png 2x\" /></a><div style=\"position: absolute; z-index: 2; top: 55.6%; left: 11.1%; height: 0; width: 0; margin: 0; padding: 0;\"><div style=\"position: relative; text-align: center; left: -5px; top: -5px; width: 10px; font-size: 10px;\"><img alt=\"The Reach and the location of Bandallon\" src=\"/images/thumb/b/b4/Red_pog.png/10px-Red_pog.png\" title=\"Bandallon\" width=\"10\" height=\"10\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/b/b4/Red_pog.png/15px-Red_pog.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/b/b4/Red_pog.png/20px-Red_pog.png 2x\" /></div><div style=\"font-size: 100%; line-height: 110%; z-index:90; position: relative; top: -1.5em; width: 6em; top:-0.15em; left: -3em; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"padding: 1px;\"><b>Bandallon</b></span></div></div></div>\n<div class=\"thumbcaption\"><a href=\"/index.php/The_Reach\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"The Reach\">The Reach</a> and the location of Bandallon\n</div>\n</div>\n</div><table>\n\n<tbody><tr><td></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Bandallon</b> is the seat of <a href=\"/index.php/House_Blackbar\" title=\"House Blackbar\">House Blackbar</a> in the <a href=\"/index.php/Reach\" title=\"Reach\">Reach</a>. It is located on the shores of the <a href=\"/index.php/Sunset_Sea\" title=\"Sunset Sea\">Sunset Sea</a>,<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rawoiafbandallon.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rawoiafbandallon.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> west of <a href=\"/index.php/Brightwater_Keep\" title=\"Brightwater Keep\">Brightwater Keep</a>, northwest of <a href=\"/index.php/Oldtown\" title=\"Oldtown\">Oldtown</a>, and southwest of the <a href=\"/index.php/Shield_Islands\" title=\"Shield Islands\">Shield Islands</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Bandallon&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>After the election of <a href=\"/index.php/Septon\" title=\"Septon\">Septon</a> <a href=\"/index.php/Alfyn\" title=\"Alfyn\">Alfyn</a> to the seat of <a href=\"/index.php/High_Septon\" title=\"High Septon\">High Septon</a>, King <a href=\"/index.php/Jaehaerys_I_Targaryen\" title=\"Jaehaerys I Targaryen\">Jaehaerys I Targaryen</a> visited Bandallon, <a href=\"/index.php/Three_Towers\" title=\"Three Towers\">Three Towers</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Uplands\" title=\"Uplands\">Uplands</a>, and <a href=\"/index.php/Honeyholt\" title=\"Honeyholt\">Honeyholt</a> while awaiting the arrival of the ailing Alfyn to <a href=\"/index.php/Oldtown\" title=\"Oldtown\">Oldtown</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabbirth.2C_death.2C_and_betrayal_under_king_jaehaerys_i.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabbirth.2C_death.2C_and_betrayal_under_king_jaehaerys_i.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>In <a href=\"/index.php/Years_after_Aegon%27s_Conquest#Year_89_After_the_Conquest\" title=\"Years after Aegon&#39;s Conquest\">89&#160;AC</a>, King Jaehaerys I stopped at Bandallon during one of his <a href=\"/index.php/Royal_progress\" title=\"Royal progress\">progress</a> around the <a href=\"/index.php/Reach\" title=\"Reach\">Reach</a>. As Jaehaerys was <a href=\"/index.php/First_Quarrel\" title=\"First Quarrel\">estranged</a> from his sister-wife, Queen <a href=\"/index.php/Alysanne_Targaryen\" title=\"Alysanne Targaryen\">Alysanne Targaryen</a>, at the time, Lord <a href=\"/index.php/House_Blackbar\" title=\"House Blackbar\">Blackbar</a>'s youngest daughter boldly tried to seduce the king. Jaehaerys refused her advances, however.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabthe_long_reign_-_jaehaerys_and_alysanne:_policy.2C_progeny.2C_and_pain.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabthe_long_reign_-_jaehaerys_and_alysanne:_policy.2C_progeny.2C_and_pain.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>While sailing against Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Dalton_Greyjoy\" title=\"Dalton Greyjoy\">Dalton Greyjoy</a> in the <a href=\"/index.php/Westerlands\" title=\"Westerlands\">westerlands</a> in <a href=\"/index.php/133_AC\" title=\"133 AC\">133&#160;AC</a>, Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Alyn_Velaryon\" title=\"Alyn Velaryon\">Alyn Velaryon</a>'s <a href=\"/index.php/Velaryon_fleet\" title=\"Velaryon fleet\">fleet</a> passed Bandallon.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabunder_the_regents_-_the_voyage_of_alyn_oakenfist.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_5-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabunder_the_regents_-_the_voyage_of_alyn_oakenfist.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-5\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Bandallon&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rawoiafbandallon.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rawoiafbandallon.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_World_of_Ice_and_Fire\" title=\"A World of Ice and Fire\">George R. R. Martin's A World of Ice and Fire</a></i>, Bandallon.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-2\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows\" title=\"A Feast for Crows\">A Feast for Crows</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows-Map_of_the_South\" title=\"A Feast for Crows-Map of the South\">Map of the South</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rfabbirth.2C_death.2C_and_betrayal_under_king_jaehaerys_i.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfabbirth.2C_death.2C_and_betrayal_under_king_jaehaerys_i.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/Fire_%26_Blood\" title=\"Fire &amp; Blood\">F